-- Environment in Pike River Coal Mine Remains Unsafe, New Zealand Police Say
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 2010-11-23T21:22:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/environment-in-pike-river-coal-mine-remains-unsafe-new-zealand-police-say.html
New Zealand Police Superintendent
Gary Knowles said the environment in the Pike River Coal Co.
mine, where 29 men are missing underground, remains unsafe. He
spoke at a press conference today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
